reviewText: Quality of the transfer was good, and the Blu ray was sharp and colors were bright.  As to the movie itself, you either like this 70's exploitation type film or you don't.  However, if you are looking for a copy with a very good picture, this  German version does not disappoint.  No problems playing it on a North American player.  It is a blu Ray, so a blu Ray or 4k player is needed.
